{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/film-sensei-kunshu-tayang-di-jepang/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Film Live Action Sensei Kunshu Tayang di Jepang Agustus Mendatang","content":"<p>Jepang begitu menghargai hubungan profesional yang terjalin, baik sesame rekan kerja, atasan dengan bawahan, juga antara guru dan siswa. Meskipun demikian, penerapan profesionalisme terganggu ketika bicara urusan cinta. Ada perusahaan yang tidak mempekerjakan karyawan yang merupakan pasangan suami-istri demi alasan profesionalisme. Meskipun demikian, banyak yang mengakalinya dengan cara tidak menikah.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48013\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48013\" data-attachment-id=\"48013\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-sensei-kunshu-tayang-di-jepang/attachment/01-sensei-kunshu/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-sensei-kunshu.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-sensei-kunshu\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-sensei-kunshu-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-sensei-kunshu.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48013\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-sensei-kunshu.jpg\" alt=\"Poster Film Sensei Kunshu (Sumber: Asianwiki)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-sensei-kunshu.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-sensei-kunshu-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48013\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Poster Film Sensei Kunshu (Sumber: Asianwiki)</p></div></p>\n<p>Di ranah pendidikan, kesulitan justru terjadi lantaran siswa yang memasuki masa puber menyukai guru mereka. Perasaan kagum bisa sedemikian cepat berubah menjadi cinta. Walaupun sudah ada larangan kalau tidak boleh ada hubungan siswa dan guru, hal itu tidak menghalangi perasaan yang sudah terjalin. Akibatnya, hubungan guru dan siswa yang terkuak bisa menjadi skandal dan aib tidak hanya bagi kedua pelakunya, tapi juga bagi keluarga, sekolah, hingga orang-orang terdekat mereka.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48014\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48014\" data-attachment-id=\"48014\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-sensei-kunshu-tayang-di-jepang/attachment/02-sensei-kunshu/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-sensei-kunshu.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-sensei-kunshu\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-sensei-kunshu-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-sensei-kunshu.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48014\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-sensei-kunshu.jpg\" alt=\"Perbandingan Hiromitsu Sensei (Sumber: Eiga)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-sensei-kunshu.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-sensei-kunshu-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48014\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Perbandingan Hiromitsu Sensei (Sumber: Eiga)</p></div></p>\n<p>Hubungan terlarang antara guru dan siswa inilah yang mencoba digambarkan oleh Momoko Koda dalam manganya yang berjudul Sensei Kunshu. Manga yang pertama kali dipublikasikan di majalah manga shoujo Bessatsu Margaret pada 13 Juli 2013 hingga 13 Juni 2017 ini dicetak sejumlah 13 volume sebanyak 1.43 juta eksemplar dan mendapat apresiasi cukup baik dari pembacanya yang kebanyakan adalah wanita, sehingga mendapat adaptasi film Live-Action yang memulai syutingnya pada awal tahun 2018 ini.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48015\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48015\" data-attachment-id=\"48015\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-sensei-kunshu-tayang-di-jepang/attachment/03-sensei-kunshu/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-sensei-kunshu.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-sensei-kunshu\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-sensei-kunshu-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-sensei-kunshu.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48015\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-sensei-kunshu.jpg\" alt=\"Ayuha Samaru versi Live Action dan Manga (Sumber: Eiga)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-sensei-kunshu.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-sensei-kunshu-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48015\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ayuha Samaru versi Live Action dan Manga (Sumber: Eiga)</p></div></p>\n<p>Sensei Kunshu berkisah tentang seorang siswi SMA bernama Ayuha Samaru yang jujur dan pekerja keras dalam segala hal. Suatu ketika, dia mendapat masalah di restoran Gyudon karena lupa membawa uang. Beruntung, pria bernama Yoshitaka Hiromitsu menolong membayarkan makanannya. Keesokan harinya, Ayuha terkejut lantaran dia kembali bertemu Yoshitaka yang menjadi guru pengganti di sekolahnya. Meskipun Yoshitaka terkesan arogan, kepintarannya justru membuat rasa kekaguman Ayuha berubah menjadi cinta. Ayuha pun memutuskan untuk mendekatinya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48016\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48016\" data-attachment-id=\"48016\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-sensei-kunshu-tayang-di-jepang/attachment/04-sensei-kunshu/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-sensei-kunshu.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-sensei-kunshu\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-sensei-kunshu-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-sensei-kunshu.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48016\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-sensei-kunshu.jpg\" alt=\"Hiromitsu-Sensei mengenalkan diri. Kakkoi! (Sumber: Youtube)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-sensei-kunshu.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-sensei-kunshu-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48016\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Hiromitsu-Sensei mengenalkan diri. Kakkoi! (Sumber: Youtube)</p></div></p>\n<p>Pemilihan para pemerannya juga menambah daya tarik film bergenre romance comedy ini. Manami Hamabe, aktris cantik yang pernah berperan di film Live-Action Ajin, menjadi Ayuha Samaru, siswi SMA yang ekspresif. Manami akan beradu akting dengan Ryouma Takeuchi. Aktor yang pernah bermain di serial drama adaptasi The Girl Who Leapt Through Time ini akan menjadi Yoshitaka Hiromitsu, guru tampan dan jenius tapi arogan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48017\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48017\" data-attachment-id=\"48017\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-sensei-kunshu-tayang-di-jepang/attachment/05-sensei-kunshu/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-sensei-kunshu.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-sensei-kunshu\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-sensei-kunshu-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-sensei-kunshu.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48017\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-sensei-kunshu.jpg\" alt=\"Ayuha Samaru, kawaii! (Sumber: Youtube)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-sensei-kunshu.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-sensei-kunshu-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48017\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ayuha Samaru, kawaii! (Sumber: Youtube)</p></div></p>\n<p>Kedua tokoh utama tersebut akan didukung oleh beberapa aktor dan aktris pendukung lain. Rina Kawaei. Mantan anggota grup idol AKB48 ini akan menjadi Aoi Nakamura, teman dekat dari Ayuha. Taiki Sato, anggota boy broup EXILE, di sini mendapat peran sebagai Kotake Sawada. Ada pula Yua Shinkawa yang berperan menjadi Aika Saimon, seorang pianis teman masa kecil Yoshitaka-Sensei. Aktris pendatang baru yang merupakan jebolan dari Toho Cinderella Audition tahun 2016 lalu, Riko Fukumoto, mendapat peran sebagai Kaho.</p>\n<p>Momoko Koda yang juga menulis manga Heroine Shikkaku, menempati posisi penulis skenario dengan dibantu oleh Erika Yoshida. Posisi sutradara sendiri diduduki oleh Sho Tsukikawa, yang menyutradarai film Let Me Eat Your Pancreas dan serial Minna! Esper Dayo!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48018\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48018\" data-attachment-id=\"48018\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-sensei-kunshu-tayang-di-jepang/attachment/06-sensei-kunshu/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/06-sensei-kunshu.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-sensei-kunshu\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/06-sensei-kunshu-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/06-sensei-kunshu.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48018\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/06-sensei-kunshu.jpg\" alt=\"Para pemeran pendukung (SumberAsianwiki)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/06-sensei-kunshu.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/06-sensei-kunshu-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48018\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Para pemeran pendukung (SumberAsianwiki)</p></div></p>\n<p>Untuk musik pengiring, mungkin di antara kalian ada yang mengenal judul lagu I Want You Back. Lagu yang dipopulerkan pertama kali oleh Jackson 5 dan membantu melambungkan nama Michael Jackson di industri musik dunia itu akan dibawakan ulang oleh grup idol asal Korea Selatan, TWICE. Mau dengar lagunya seperti apa? Simak sekalian trailer filmnya berikut ini:</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/v74l9673xrY\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Karena Sensei Kunshu baru akan ditayangkan di Jepang pada tanggal 1 Agustus 2018 mendatang, harap bersabar untuk menontonnya ya. Semoga saja ada distributor film yang berniat membawa film ini untuk ditayangkan di Indonesia.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"4e42b4f7-e286-51b5-a5f3-7a9852e77246"}}}